name: stagePix_008 – 'live visuals set Ars Electronica Festival 2003’
description: Still image from live visuals set, Ars Electronica Festival, 2003, performed to accompany “Analogique A”, a musical composition by Iannis Xenakis, as part of the performance programme "Principles of Indeterminism, an Evening from Score to Code". Artwork by LIA (www.liaworks.com), 2003. Still: 2048 px × 752 px. Edition of 3 + 1AP (not minted).
